        public boolean doFilter(Session session)
        Description copied from interface: SessionFilter
        Return true, the SessionFilterChain will call the next SessionFilter if it has next SessionFilter. It will break the process if return false.
        Specified by:
        doFilter in interface SessionFilter
        Parameters:

        Returns:
